Class DescriptionBuilder.Properties

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    DescriptionBuilder

    public static final class DescriptionBuilder.Properties
extends java.lang.Object
    Properties that can be passed to a DescriptionBuilder. The property define the values used by the DescriptionBuilder.
